OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,6,FTuesday will be dry, bright and breezy
OL,7,Fwith some warm hazy sunshine. Cloudier
OL,8,Fon Wednesday, with overnight rain
OL,9,Fintroducing a colder day on Thursday
OL,10,Fwith sunshine and blustery showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
